sequenceDiagram
  participant Dev as Developer
  participant Repo as Git Repo
  participant CI as CI
  participant Registry as Docker Registry
  participant Host as Production Host

  Dev->>Repo: push code
  Repo->>CI: trigger pipeline
  CI->>CI: build & unit tests
  CI->>CI: package artifact (jar/war/build)
  CI->>CI: docker build & tag
  CI->>Registry: push image
  Host->>Registry: pull image
  Host->>Host: deploy (docker run / docker-compose / swarm)
  Host->>Users: serve application